RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unwayed
<hw>Un*wayed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not used
to travel; <as>as, colts that are <ex>unwayed</ex></as>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Suckling.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having no ways or roads; pathless.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Wyclif.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unwearied</ent>⟦br⟧
